This app and framework is being adapted from a few we resources

  PHP MVC - http://anantgarg.com/2009/03/13/write-your-own-php-mvc-framework-part-1/
  PHP Couch - http://wiki.apache.org/couchdb/Getting_started_with_PHP
  
PHP is to be used for
  - DB access
  - Authentication
  - serving json

Front end 
  - jQuery
  - jQuery UI for drag n drop
  - twitter bootstrap
  - Javascript 
